          respective owners and are used for identification only.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">5. Acceptable use</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">
          Do not use the Site to attempt unauthorized access to our systems,
          disrupt the Site's operation, or misrepresent affiliation with
